sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (browser)
    participant AS as AppSync GraphQL<br/>(JWT: tenantId·userId from claims)
    participant R as JS resolvers<br/>(direct DDB — no Lambda)
    participant DB as InboxItem<br/>(DDB PK=tenant#user)
    participant CTR as unread_ctr<br/>(same DDB item)
    participant RG as ResolutionGroup

    U->>AS: subscription onInboxEvent(me)
    Note over AS: subscription auth: userId must equal<br/>$ctx.identity — own channel only.<br/>AppSync manages the connection (no registry)

    U->>AS: query inbox(cursor, limit)
    Note over AS: tenantId from JWT — resolver builds<br/>PK=tenant#user server-side
    AS->>R: resolve
    R->>DB: Query PK=tenant#user WHERE expiresAt>now AND state IN(unread,read)
    Note over DB: visibility filter: expired never returned<br/>resolved items masked until sweep lands
    R->>CTR: GET unread_ctr (+ L1 read-time self-heal)
    AS-->>U: {items, unreadCount, nextCursor}

    U->>AS: mutation markRead(notifId)
    AS->>R: resolve
    R->>DB: CondUpdate state=unread→read (condition: state=unread)
    alt transition succeeded
        DB-->>R: ok
        R->>CTR: ADD unread_ctr -1
        Note over CTR: atomic — conditional win ensures exactly one decrement
        alt type.dismissOnRead=true
            R->>DB: CondUpdate state=read→dismissed
        end
        AS-->>U: item + BADGE event to other devices
    else already read/dismissed
        DB-->>R: ConditionalCheckFailed
        AS-->>U: current item (idempotent)
    end

    U->>AS: mutation resolve(notifId) — backup path
    Note over AS: verify item belongs to caller's tenant#user
    AS->>R: resolve
    R->>DB: GET item → verify ownership
    R->>RG: trigger group sweep
    RG->>DB: Query GSI groupKey → all items in group
    RG->>DB: BatchUpdate state=resolved × N
    RG->>CTR: ADD unread_ctr -1 × N users (conditional: was unread)
    RG->>AS: publishInboxEvent REMOVE × N + badge updates
    AS-->>U: ResolveResult
    Note over AS: audit: resolved{principal:user, path:inbox, episode}
